ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjective__dlm.name: Asset Service Level Objective
ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjective__dlm.description: The Asset Service Level Objective (SLO) DMO represents SLO data that's transmitted over a network, such as a computer network or a telecommunications network. SLO data stores details, such as source and destination IP addresses, timestamps, and data types (for example, TCP and UDP).
